Class MessageRegistry

java.lang.Object
org.tquadrat.foundation.config.internal.MessageRegistry
@UtilityClass @ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: MessageRegistry.java 1042 2022-12-26 14:05:06Z tquadrat $") @API(status=INTERNAL, since="0.1.0") public final class MessageRegistry extends Object
This class is meant as a place to hold the specific error messages for the failed conversion of command line entries.
Author:
Thomas Thrien (thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org)
